    "However, in order to describe the system under consideration in a more representative manner, the following additions and modifications were made: modification to land use (different types of land transformations are considered), mineral extraction categories (additional resources are added), and radioactive waste (radioactive waste and its occupied volume are evaluated) (Spinelli et al., 2019).",
